==San Marino==
* Country: San Marino
* Football association: [[San Marino Football Federation]]
* League: [[Campionato Sammarinese di Calcio|Sammarinese Football Championship]] ({{lang-it|Campionato Sammarinese di Calcio}})
* UEFA ranking: 54th<ref name=coefficient2018/>
* Soccerway profile: [https://int.soccerway.com/national/san-marino/ here]

This is a complete list of football clubs in San Marino (as San Marino has only one level domestic amateur league), apart from [[San Marino Calcio]], the only professional Sammarinese club, which as of [[2016–17 Serie D|2016–17]] competes in [[Serie D]], the fourth level of the [[Italian football league system]].

